Style Sheet Creation Utility

Before you do anything read "Manual.pdf"

Use this utility to create a style sheet for your site. This controls the fonts, colours and general appearence of your pages

The default styles are displayed in the form below. Make any changes you require then press the "Create Style Sheet" button. After you have saved the style check the results with the Style Viewer. When you are satisfied with the results move the file to ..\Webwright\Blpro\Style\ subdirectory.
